channel.title: Weird model problem
channel.description:
Hey, I have just added a new model. I can assure you I have done 99% of things correctly. The new model is a platebody, and when I wear it my arms and hands are about 1 meter behind my body. They are animated fine... but I just can't figure out where the problem is. If anyone knows how to fix this I would greatly appreciate it.
P.S. I will post a picture tomorrow.
Thanks in advance. ~~ 14-08
